name: CoreAPI Run_Translation
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Run_Translation Details
about:
Description

Planet 9-Run_Translation manages the list of Planet 9 launchpads (enabled with Translation)

API Run_Translation is the Planet 9 API to access the translation enabled launchpad and the operations performed on them.

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the API Run_Translation.

Operations Performed

Get

Get the selected launchpad tile and tile group fields

RequestID
ResponseGet(Object)- Definition            


List

Get the list of the launchpads with enabled translation

ResponseList(array)- Definition               

Save

Save the translation for the launchpad tile groups and tiles

RequestSave(object)- Definition
